<DATE>09/12/2008</DATE>
<AUTHOR>John</AUTHOR>
<TEXT>The driver's seat is very comfortable, the car drives good, rides good, and wind and road noise is minimal. The fuel economy is very good. The right rear speaker is defective, a new one has been ordered. One negative design flaw is that the arm-rest between the driver and front passenger seats has to be raised up in order to set or release the parking brake. A telescoping steering wheel would be greatly appreciated by long legged drivers such as myselg.</TEXT>
<FAVORITE>OnStar, XM radio, mp3 CD capability, hands free calling.</FAVORITE>
